<body>
  <div class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>IT Consulting & Technical Advisory</h1>
      <p>I help companies design, build, and optimize software solutions with a focus on reliability, scalability, and business value.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn">Contact me</a>
