    <section class="section" id="about">
      <h2>About</h2>
      <p>I am an independent IT consultant registered as an Individual Entrepreneur in Georgia and a Georgian tax resident.</p>
      <p>Although I currently reside in Armenia, I work remotely with clients worldwide, providing high‑level technical advisory and consulting services.</p>
      <p>My focus is on helping businesses make better technical decisions, improve their systems, and deliver software more efficiently.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="services">
      <h2>Services</h2>
      <p>Core services include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Technical consulting and architecture review</li>
        <li>System design and solution planning</li>
        <li>Performance optimization and scalability</li>
        <li>Code and infrastructure review</li>
        <li>Ongoing technical advisory and mentoring</li>
      </ul>
      <p>I work with startups, product companies, and service businesses that rely on technology to grow.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="how">
      <h2>How I work</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>We start with a discovery call to understand your goals and current challenges</li>
        <li>I analyze your systems, processes, and requirements</li>
        <li>I provide clear recommendations and an implementation roadmap</li>
        <li>If needed, I stay involved as a long‑term technical advisor</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="clients">
      <h2>Clients & Geography</h2>
      <p>I work remotely with clients from:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>United States</li>
        <li>European Union</li>
